"cat": "personas",
"id": "ai-systems-engineer",
"title": "ai-systems-engineer",
"summary": "Owns the AI surface — tier allocation, prompt/tool-description/skill as contract, eval design, grounding/hallucination, non-determinism containment, model drift, and inference cost. Hard veto on an AI capability with no eval harness or…",
"path": "pack/adapters/claude-code/agents/ai-systems-engineer.md",
